REALLY, REALLY BORED.

00:00:24.110 --> 00:00:26.289
NARRATOR (CONT’D)
Paranormal Activity.

00:00:26.289 --> 00:00:29.919
NARRATOR (CONT’D)
Get ready to experience the cheaper, less

00:00:29.919 --> 00:00:33.260
interesting version
of The Blair Witch Project.

00:00:33.260 --> 00:00:39.750
NARRATOR (CONT’D)
Behold the terror of a film so easy, anyone’s

00:00:39.750 --> 00:00:40.949
