00:00:45.760 --> 00:00:49.120
NARRATOR (CONT’D)
Prepare to be terrified...

00:00:49.120 --> 00:00:56.210
By a marketing department so effective, they
actually made cities demand this tedious home

00:00:56.210 --> 00:00:57.210
movie...

00:00:57.210 --> 00:00:59.470
NARRATOR (CONT’D)
