00:01:02.789 --> 00:01:04.440
least five more movies.

00:01:04.440 --> 00:01:07.430
NARRATOR (CONT’D)
A movie for an audience so gullible...

00:01:07.430 --> 00:01:10.560
NARRATOR (CONT’D)
